svg.text: Third Level: Becomes more private with restricted access to the Great Hall. Still with an open foyer and an outdoor terrace.
Street Level: completely open to the city.
Long section showing a Public - Private distribution.
Sixth Level: Large outdoor terrace open to the public.
Fifth Level: Private rooms for administration and Workshops with restricted access.
Second Level: Open, without direct eyesight from the street and with some private rooms.
